text: Nikolay Voronkov (born 1883, date of death unknown) was a Russian swimmer. He competed in the men's 400 metre freestyle event at the 1912 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1883 births Category:Year of death missing Category:Russian male swimmers Category:Olympic swimmers of Russia Category:Swimmers at the 1912 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Vilnius
